---

<SiteLayout
  title="【既卒生】2027年度医学部合格へ。鬼監理×鬼特訓の「レクサスプレミア本科」｜医学部受験ならLEXUS（レクサス教育センター）"
  description="【既卒生対象・2027年度入試対応】医学部予備校レクサス教育センター「レクサスプレミア本科」のコース紹介です。「鬼監理×鬼特訓」による徹底的な学習管理と実践指導で、医学部逆転合格を「奇跡」から「必然」へ変えます。カリキュラム、学費、合格実績、専用寮の詳細はこちら。"
  canonical="https://lexus-ec.com/lexus-premier/"
  ogImage={seo.ogImage}
>
  <main class="premier-page">
    <section class="premier-cinematic-hero" data-premier-cinematic-hero>
      <video
        class="premier-cinematic-hero__video"
        src={premierHeroVideos[0]}
        muted
        playsinline
        preload="metadata"
        data-src={premierHeroVideos[0]}
        data-playlist={premierHeroVideos.join("|")}
      ></video>
      <div class="premier-cinematic-hero__fallback" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="premier-cinematic-hero__shade" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="content premier-cinematic-hero__inner">
        <div class="premier-fireline-stage">
          <div class="premier-fireline-act premier-fireline-act--first" aria-label="レクサス・プレミア本科">
            <p class="premier-fireline-prime premier-fireline-first-item"><span class="premier-fireline-nowrap">PREMIERE MAINE COURSE</span></p>
            <p class="premier-fireline-subtitle premier-fireline-first-item">医学部特化のオールインワン</p>
          </div>

          <div class="premier-fireline-corner-mark" aria-hidden="true">
            <img src={penLogo} alt="" width="300" height="300" decoding="async" />
            <span>PREMIERE MAINE COURSE</span>
            <strong>レクサスプレミア本科</strong>
          </div>

          <div class="premier-fireline-act premier-fireline-act--second" aria-label="レクサス・プレミア本科 メッセージ">
            <div class="premier-fireline-quote-stack">
              <span>「今年で決める！」</span>
              <span>「もうサボらない」</span>
              <span>「厳しい環境に身を置こう」</span>
            </div>
            <p class="premier-fireline-year">2027年度入試対応 / 既卒生対象</p>
            <h1 class="premier-fireline-title">その覚悟に、<br /><strong>レクサスが応える。</strong></h1>
            <p class="premier-fireline-lead">授業、演習、質問対応、学習監理、生活環境まで。合格に必要な行動を、曖昧な努力で終わらせないための医学部受験フルコースです。</p>
            <div class="premier-fireline-meta" aria-label="レクサス・プレミア本科の概要">
              <span>レクサス・プレミア本科</span>
              <span>4月開講</span>
              <span>募集期間 2/1(日)-4/5(日)</span>
              <span>定員になり次第終了</span>
            </div>
            <div class="premier-fireline-actions">
              <a class="button button--red" href="/request-documents/">資料請求する</a>
              <a class="button button--blue" href="/reservation/">個別説明会へ</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="premier-ideal" aria-labelledby="premier-ideal-title">
      <div class="content">
        <SectionHeading id="premier-ideal-title" label="IDEAL FORM" title="医学部合格への 理想形。" />
        <p class="premier-ideal__lead">
          レクサス・プレミア本科は、授業を受けるだけのコースではありません。学習管理、質問対応、夜間演習、出願戦略、生活リズムまでを一体化し、医学部合格に必要な行動を毎日積み上げるための環境です。
        </p>
        <div class="premier-ideal-grid">
          <article>
            <span>01</span>
            <h3>“鬼監理”で迷わせない</h3>
            <p>学習計画、課題、復習、確認テストを講師側が把握し、今日やるべきことを具体化します。</p>
          </article>
          <article>
            <span>02</span>
            <h3>“鬼特訓”で逃がさない</h3>
            <p>授業後の演習と質問対応を重ね、分かったつもりを実戦で使える状態まで引き上げます。</p>
          </article>
          <article>
            <span>03</span>
            <h3>寮と校舎を一体化</h3>
            <p>移動時間と生活の乱れを減らし、医学部受験に集中するための学習生活を設計します。</p>
          </article>
        </div>
        <div class="premier-ideal__actions">
          <a class="button button--blue" href="/study-support-system/">“鬼監理”を詳しく見る</a>
          <a class="button button--red" href="/medical-english-training/">英語の鬼特訓</a>
          <a class="button button--red" href="/medical-math-training/">数学の鬼特訓</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="premier-achievement" aria-labelledby="premier-achievement-title">
      <div class="content">
        <SectionHeading id="premier-achievement-title" label="ACHIEVEMENT" title="2025年度の実績報告" subtitle="〜 一年で合格する割合 〜" />
        <p class="premier-achievement__intro">
          スタートラインは一人ひとり違っても、合格に必要な行動量と精度を毎日積み上げる。その結果を、入学時の偏差値帯ごとに整理しました。
        </p>
        <div class="premier-result-panel" aria-label="2025年度 医学部医学科 入試合格実績">
          <div class="premier-result-panel__head">
            <div>
              <span class="premier-result-panel__eyebrow">2025 ENTRANCE EXAM</span>
              <p><span>スタートライン別・</span><span>医学部医学科合格率</span></p>
            </div>
            <strong>医学部医学科のみ</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="premier-result-list">
            {achievementRows.map((row, index) => (
              <article
                class={`premier-result-row premier-result-row--${row.tone}`}
                style={`--rate: ${row.rate}%; --order: ${index};`}
                aria-label={`${row.start}から${row.result}、${row.detail}`}
              >
                <div class="premier-result-row__start">
                  <span>START</span>
                  <strong>{row.start}</strong>
                </div>
                <div class="premier-result-row__meter" aria-hidden="true">
                  <span></span>
                </div>
                <div class="premier-result-row__result">
                  <span>RESULT</span>
                  <strong>{row.result}</strong>
                  <em>{row.detail}</em>
                </div>
              </article>
            ))}
          </div>
          <p class="premier-result-note">※ すべて医学部医学科の合格実績です。</p>
        </div>
        <h3 class="university-list__title">累計合格実績</h3>
        <div class="achievement-stats">
          {achievementStats.map((stat) => (
            <article class={`stat-card stat-card--${stat.tone}`}>
              <p>{stat.label}</p>
              <strong>{stat.value}</strong>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
        <h3 class="university-list__title">合格した大学一覧 (医学部医学科のみ)</h3>
        <ul class="university-list" aria-label="医学部入試過去6年分の最終合格者データ">
          {acceptedUniversities.flat().map((result) => (
            <li>
              <span>{result.name}</span>
              <strong>{result.count}</strong>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <p class="note">※過去6年分 (2021～2026年度) の最終合格者データ</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="premier-feature" aria-labelledby="premier-feature-title">
      <div class="content">
        <SectionHeading id="premier-feature-title" label="METHOD" title="プレミア本科の特徴" />
        <div class="premier-feature__statement" aria-label="鬼監理×鬼特訓">
          <p>偶然や奇跡に頼らない逆転劇。</p>
          <p class="premier-feature__mark">
            <span>鬼監理</span><span class="premier-feature__mark-x" aria-hidden="true">×</span><span>鬼特訓</span>
          </p>
          <p>その先にある、絶対の合格へ。</p>
        </div>
        <p class="premier-feature__lead">迷わせず、逃がさず、合格まで伴走します。</p>
        <div class="premier-feature-grid">
          {featureCards.map((card) => (
            <article class="pillar-card">
              <div class="pillar-card__head">
                <img src={card.image} alt="" width="234" height="260" loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-hidden="true" />
                <h3 class="pillar-card__title">{card.title}</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="pillar-card__subtitle">
                {card.lead.split("×").map((part, i) => (
                  <Fragment>
                    {i > 0 && <span class="pillar-card__times" aria-hidden="true">×</span>}
                    <span>{part.trim()}</span>
                  </Fragment>
                ))}
              </p>
              <p class="pillar-card__body">{card.body}</p>
              <p class="pillar-card__cue" aria-hidden="true">↓ 詳しくはコチラ ↓</p>
              <div class="pillar-card__actions">
                {card.links.map((link) => <a class="pillar-card__button" href={link.href}>{link.label}</a>)}
              </div>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
        <div class="premier-feature__closing">
          <p>もしあなたが、今の学習環境に限界を感じているのなら、</p>
          <p>このコースこそが <span>突破口</span> となります。</p>
          <p>あなたを1年間、合格のためだけに突き進む <span>勉強の鬼</span> へと変える、</p>
          <p>「特訓プログラム」です。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="premier-overview" aria-labelledby="premier-overview-title">
      <div class="content">
        <SectionHeading id="premier-overview-title" label="OVERVIEW" title="プレミア本科の概要" />
        <section class="premier-overview-block premier-overview-block--classes" aria-labelledby="premier-classes-title">
          <header class="premier-overview-subhead">
            <p>CLASS DESIGN</p>
            <h3 id="premier-classes-title">クラス一覧</h3>
            <small><span>現在地を見極め、上位クラスへの昇格まで見据えます。</span><span>授業・演習・夜間トレーニングを一体設計します。</span></small>
          </header>
          <div class="premier-class-board" aria-label="プレミア本科 クラス一覧">
          {classTiers.map((tier) => (
            <>
              <article class={`premier-class-card premier-class-card--${tier.tone}`}>
                <div class="premier-class-card__status">
                  <span class="premier-class-card__mark" aria-hidden="true">{tier.letter}</span>
                  <div class="premier-class-card__identity">
                    <p>{tier.label}</p>
                    <em>{tier.letter}{tier.word}</em>
                  </div>
                  <strong class="premier-class-card__target">{tier.target}</strong>
                </div>
                <div class="premier-class-card__body">
                  <div class="premier-class-card__head">
                    <h4>{tier.title}<span>【{tier.category}】</span></h4>
                  </div>
                  <ul class="premier-class-card__programs" aria-label={`${tier.title}の授業構成`}>
                    {tier.programs.map((program) => <li>{program}</li>)}
                  </ul>
                  <p class="premier-class-card__summary">{tier.summary}</p>
                </div>
              </article>
              {tier.upgrade && (
                <div class={`premier-class-bridge premier-class-bridge--${tier.tone}`}>
                  <span class="premier-class-bridge__arrows" aria-hidden="true">
                    <span></span>
                    <span></span>
                    <span></span>
                  </span>
                  <p>{tier.upgrade}</p>
                </div>
              )}
            </>
          ))}
          </div>
        </section>
        <section class="premier-overview-block premier-overview-block--roadmap" aria-labelledby="premier-roadmap-title">
          <header class="premier-overview-subhead">
            <p>YEAR ROADMAP</p>
            <h3 id="premier-roadmap-title">年間計画イメージ</h3>
            <small>学力レベル・対応大学・クラス進行を、1年の伸び方として俯瞰できます。</small>
          </header>
          <section class="premier-annual-plan" aria-label="2026レクサスプレミア本科 年間計画">
          <div class="premier-annual-plan__head">
            <div>
              <p class="premier-annual-plan__eyebrow">YEAR ROADMAP</p>
              <h4>現在地と、1年後の到達ラインを同じスケールで見る。</h4>
            </div>
            <p>学力レベル0〜11を基準に、対応大学の目安とクラス別の進行を整理しました。横に追うほど、各クールでどこまで引き上げるかが見える設計です。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="premier-annual-plan__legend" aria-label="クラス色の凡例">
            <span class="premier-annual-plan__legend-item premier-annual-plan__legend-item--red">Sクラス</span>
            <span class="premier-annual-plan__legend-item premier-annual-plan__legend-item--gold">Aクラス</span>
            <span class="premier-annual-plan__legend-item premier-annual-plan__legend-item--green">Fクラス</span>
            <span class="premier-annual-plan__legend-line">昇格目安</span>
          </div>
          <div class="premier-annual-plan__scroll" tabindex="0" aria-label="学力レベル別の対応大学一覧。横にスクロールできます。">
            <div class="premier-level-matrix">
              <div class="premier-level-matrix__label">学力レベル</div>
              {annualLevels.map((item) => (
                <div class="premier-level-tab" aria-label={`学力レベル${item.level} ${item.label}`}>
                  <span class="premier-level-tab__number">{item.level}</span>
                  <span class="premier-level-tab__label">
                    {(annualLevelLabelLines[item.level] ?? [item.label]).map((line) => <span>{line}</span>)}
                  </span>
                </div>
              ))}
              <div class="premier-level-matrix__label premier-level-matrix__label--body"><span>対応レベル</span></div>
              {annualLevels.map((item) => (
                <article class="premier-level-card">
                  {item.schools.length > 0 ? (
                    <ul>
                      {item.schools.map((school) => <li>{school}</li>)}
                    </ul>
                  ) : (
                    <p>医学部受験に向けた基礎体力を作る期間</p>
                  )}
                </article>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="premier-annual-plan__scroll premier-annual-plan__scroll--roadmap" tabindex="0" aria-label="クラス別の年間進行ロードマップ。横にスクロールできます。">
            <div class="premier-roadmap">
              <div class="premier-roadmap__scale">
                <div class="premier-roadmap__scale-label">クラス進行</div>
                {annualLevels.map((item) => (
                  <span class="premier-roadmap__level">
                    <small>レベル</small>
                    <strong>{item.level}</strong>
                  </span>
                ))}
              </div>
              {annualTracks.map((track) => (
                <article
                  class={`premier-roadmap-row premier-roadmap-row--${track.tone}`}
                  style={`--row-height: ${roadmapRowHeight(track.bars.length)}px;`}
                >
                  <div class="premier-roadmap-row__label">
                    <div class="premier-roadmap-row__mark" aria-hidden="true">
                      <span>{track.letter}</span><em>{track.word}</em>
                    </div>
                    <p>{track.lane}</p>
                    <strong>{track.title}</strong>
                    <small>【{track.category}】</small>
                    <b>{track.target}</b>
                    <span class="premier-roadmap-row__summary-mobile">{track.summary}</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="premier-roadmap-row__lane">
                    {track.promotions.map((point) => (
                      <span
                        class="premier-roadmap-row__promotion"
                        style={`--left: ${planPercent(point)};`}
                        aria-hidden="true"
                      ></span>
                    ))}
                    {track.bars.map((bar, index) => (
                      <span
                        class="premier-roadmap-row__bar"
                        style={`--left: ${planPercent(bar.start)}; --width: ${planPercent(bar.end - bar.start)}; --top: ${roadmapBarTop(index, track.bars.length)}px;`}
                        aria-label={`${track.lane} ${bar.label} ${bar.period} 学力レベル${bar.start}から${bar.end}へ`}
                      >
                        <span>{bar.label}</span>
                        <em>{bar.period}</em>
                      </span>
                    ))}
                    <p>{track.summary}</p>
                  </div>
                </article>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
          </section>
        </section>
        <section class="premier-overview-block premier-overview-block--weekly" aria-labelledby="premier-weekly-title">
          <header class="premier-overview-subhead">
            <p>WEEKLY ROUTINE</p>
            <h3 id="premier-weekly-title">週間予定イメージ</h3>
            <small>朝の確認テストから夜の鬼特訓まで、学習量を生活リズムごと固定します。</small>
          </header>
          <section class="premier-week-table" aria-label="プレミア本科 週間予定イメージ">
          <div class="premier-week-table__head">
            <div>
              <p>WEEKLY ROUTINE</p>
              <h4>朝の確認テストから、夜の鬼特訓まで。</h4>
            </div>
            <p>毎日テスト、インプット授業、アウトプット演習、夜間トレーニングを1日の流れに固定。学習量を気分任せにせず、生活リズムごと合格へ寄せます。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="premier-week-table__legend" aria-label="時間割の区分">
            <span class="premier-week-table__legend-item premier-week-table__legend-item--test">
              <span class="premier-week-table__legend-token">
                <span class="premier-week-table__legend-label">テスト</span>
              </span>
              <span class="premier-week-table__legend-meaning">= 復習テスト（解き直しまでサポート）</span>
            </span>
            <span class="premier-week-table__legend-item premier-week-table__legend-item--input">
              <span class="premier-week-table__legend-token">
                <span class="premier-week-table__legend-label">インプット</span>
              </span>
              <span class="premier-week-table__legend-meaning">= クラス授業（レベル別 / 少人数制）</span>
            </span>
            <span class="premier-week-table__legend-item premier-week-table__legend-item--output">
              <span class="premier-week-table__legend-token">
                <span class="premier-week-table__legend-label">アウトプット</span>
              </span>
              <span class="premier-week-table__legend-meaning">= クラス演習（レベル別 / 少人数制）</span>
            </span>
            <span class="premier-week-table__legend-item premier-week-table__legend-item--training">
              <span class="premier-week-table__legend-token">
                <span class="premier-week-table__legend-label">夜間トレーニング</span>
              </span>
              <span class="premier-week-table__legend-meaning">= 課題＋演習質問し放題</span>
            </span>
            <span class="premier-week-table__legend-item premier-week-table__legend-item--self">
              <span class="premier-week-table__legend-token">
                <span class="premier-week-table__legend-label">自習・質問</span>
              </span>
              <span class="premier-week-table__legend-meaning">= 元気な生徒が自由参加</span>
            </span>
          </div>
          <div class="premier-week-table__scroll" tabindex="0" aria-label="週間予定表。縦横にスクロールできます。">
            <table class="premier-week-schedule">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="col">時限 / 時間</th>
                  {weekDays.map((day) => <th scope="col">{day}</th>)}
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                {weeklyScheduleRows.map((row) => (
                  row.kind === "break" ? (
                    <tr class={`premier-week-schedule__break premier-week-schedule__break--${row.tone}`}>
                      <th scope="row" colspan="8">
                        <span class="premier-week-schedule__break-label">{row.label}</span>
                        {row.note && <small class="premier-week-schedule__break-note">（{row.note}）</small>}
                      </th>
                    </tr>
                  ) : (
                    <tr class={`premier-week-schedule__period premier-week-schedule__period--${row.tone}`}>
                      <th scope="row">
                        <span>{row.period}</span>
                        <small>{row.time}</small>
                      </th>
                      {row.cells.map((cell) => (
                        <td class={weeklyCellClass(cell)}>
                          {cell.subjects && (
                            <div class="premier-week-cell__subjects" aria-label="科目">
                              {cell.subjects.map((subject) => <span>{subject}</span>)}
                            </div>
                          )}
                          {cell.label ? <strong>{cell.label}</strong> : <span class="premier-week-cell__blank">-</span>}
                          {cell.note && <em>{cell.note}</em>}
                        </td>
                      ))}
                    </tr>
                  )
                ))}
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <ul class="premier-week-table__notes">
            {weeklyScheduleNotes.map((note) => <li>{note}</li>)}
          </ul>
          </section>
        </section>
        <section class="premier-overview-block premier-overview-block--support" aria-labelledby="premier-support-title">
          <header class="premier-overview-subhead">
            <p>SUPPORT</p>
            <h3 id="premier-support-title">サポート内容 一覧</h3>
            <small>授業外の管理・相談・演習環境まで、合格に必要な行動を支えます。</small>
          </header>
          <ul class="premier-support-grid">
            {supportItems.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
          </ul>
        </section>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="premier-learning" aria-labelledby="premier-learning-title">
      <div class="content">
        <SectionHeading id="premier-learning-title" label="SYSTEM" title="学習システム" />
        <div class="premier-learning-grid">
          {learningSystems.map((item) => (
            <article>
              <span>{item.label}</span>
              <h3>{item.title}</h3>
              <p>{item.body}</p>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="premier-message" aria-labelledby="premier-message-title">
      <div class="content premier-message__box">
        <div>
          <p class="premier-message__label">MESSAGE</p>
          <h2 id="premier-message-title">お約束します。</h2>
          <p class="premier-message__statement">本コースの環境に食らいつき、私たちが敷いたレールを走り切った先には、必ず「医学部合格」という現実が待っています。</p>
          <h3>“今年で絶対に終わらせる”</h3>
          <p>その強い覚悟があるのなら、私たちは全身全霊をかけて、あなたを医師への道へと押し上げます。</p>
        </div>
        <img src={messageImage} alt="レクサス教育センター副代表 川島友紀 授業風景" width="900" height="900" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="premier-contact">
      <div class="content">
        <p>丁寧にご説明します。</p>
        <h2>まずは、お問合せください。</h2>
        <div class="premier-hero__actions">
          <a class="button button--red" href="/request-documents/">資料請求する</a>
          <a class="button button--blue" href="/reservation/">個別説明会へ</a>
        </div>
        <div class="premier-quick-actions">
          {quickLinks.map((action) => <a class={`button button--${action.tone}`} href={action.href}>{action.label}</a>)}
        </div>
        <p class="premier-contact__tel">【お急ぎでしたら、お電話ください】<br /><strong>03-3477-1306</strong><br />受付時間：10時00分〜21時00分</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="premier-extra" id="premier-selection">
      <div class="content premier-extra__grid">
        <article>
          <h2>特待生募集中</h2>
          <img src={selectionImage} alt="特待生選抜テストのお知らせ" width="1024" height="1024" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
          <a class="button button--blue" href="/test-entry/">選抜テストに申し込む</a>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h2>【さらに集中したい方へ】<br />レクサス専用寮に入居可能。<br />「10ヶ月合宿プラン」</h2>
          <img src={gardenImage} alt="レクサスガーデン外観" width="900" height="600" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
          <p>地方在住の方、実家の甘えを断ち切りたい方へ。東京渋谷の高級住宅街に佇む、専用寮をご用意しました。</p>
          <a class="button button--green" href="/top/lexus-garden/">設備や費用を見てみる</a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="premier-info" aria-labelledby="premier-info-title">
      <div class="content">
        <SectionHeading id="premier-info-title" label="NEW" title="最新 医学部受験情報" />
        <div class="premier-info-grid">
          {infoPosts.map((post) => (
            <article>
              <h3><a href={post.href}>{post.title}</a></h3>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script is:inline>
    (function () {
      var root = document.documentElement;
      var hero = document.querySelector ? document.querySelector("[data-premier-cinematic-hero]") : null;

      var hasClass = function (element, name) {
        return (" " + element.className + " ").indexOf(" " + name + " ") > -1;
      };
      var addClass = function (element, name) {
        if (!element || hasClass(element, name)) return;
        element.className = element.className ? element.className + " " + name : name;
      };
      var removeClass = function (element, name) {
        if (!element) return;
        element.className = (" " + element.className + " ")
          .replace(" " + name + " ", " ")
          .replace(/^\s+|\s+$/g, "");
      };
      var toggleClass = function (element, name, force) {
        if (force) addClass(element, name);
        else removeClass(element, name);
      };

      addClass(root, "premier-page-active");

      var syncHeader = function () {
        var scrollY = window.pageYOffset || document.documentElement.scrollTop || 0;
        toggleClass(root, "premier-nav-visible", scrollY > 96);
      };

      syncHeader();
      if (window.addEventListener) window.addEventListener("scroll", syncHeader, false);

      if (!hero || !document.createElement) return;

      var prefersReducedMotion = false;
      if (window.matchMedia) {
        prefersReducedMotion = window.matchMedia("(prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)").matches;
      }
      if (prefersReducedMotion) return;

      var styleProbe = document.createElement("div").style;
      var canAnimate = ("animation" in styleProbe || "webkitAnimation" in styleProbe)
        && ("transform" in styleProbe || "webkitTransform" in styleProbe);
      if (!canAnimate) return;

      addClass(root, "premier-enhanced");

      var video = hero.getElementsByTagName("video")[0];
      var raf = window.requestAnimationFrame || function (callback) {
        return window.setTimeout(callback, 16);
      };

      raf(function () {
        raf(function () {
          addClass(hero, "is-active");
        });
      });

      if (!video) return;

      var videoProbe = document.createElement("video");
      var canVideo = Boolean(videoProbe.canPlayType && videoProbe.canPlayType("video/mp4"));
      if (!canVideo) return;

      var playlistAttribute = video.getAttribute("data-playlist")
        || video.getAttribute("data-src")
        || video.getAttribute("src")
        || "";
      var rawPlaylist = playlistAttribute.split("|");
      var playlist = [];
      for (var i = 0; i < rawPlaylist.length; i += 1) {
        var source = rawPlaylist[i].replace(/^\s+|\s+$/g, "");
        if (source) playlist.push(source);
      }

      if (!playlist.length) return;

      var warmedVideos = {};
      var currentIndex = 0;

      var warmVideo = function (source) {
        if (!source || warmedVideos[source]) return;
        warmedVideos[source] = true;
        var head = document.head || document.getElementsByTagName("head")[0];
        if (!head) return;
        var link = document.createElement("link");
        link.rel = "prefetch";
        link.as = "video";
        link.href = source;
        head.appendChild(link);
      };

      var setVideoSource = function (index) {
        currentIndex = index % playlist.length;
        warmedVideos[playlist[currentIndex]] = true;
        if (video.getAttribute("src") !== playlist[currentIndex]) {
          video.setAttribute("src", playlist[currentIndex]);
          video.load();
        }
      };

      var loaded = false;
      var onLoaded = function () {
        if (loaded) return;
        loaded = true;
        addClass(hero, "is-video-ready");
        warmVideo(playlist[(currentIndex + 1) % playlist.length]);
        if (video.removeEventListener) video.removeEventListener("loadeddata", onLoaded, false);
      };

      video.loop = playlist.length <= 1;
      if (video.addEventListener) {
        video.addEventListener("loadeddata", onLoaded, false);
        video.addEventListener("ended", function () {
          if (playlist.length <= 1) return;
          setVideoSource(currentIndex + 1);
          warmVideo(playlist[(currentIndex + 1) % playlist.length]);
          var nextPlay = video.play && video.play();
          if (nextPlay && nextPlay.catch) nextPlay.catch(function () {});
        }, false);
      }

      setVideoSource(0);
      if (video.readyState >= 2) onLoaded();

      var playVideo = function () {
        if (!video.play) return;
        var promise = video.play();
        if (promise && promise.catch) promise.catch(function () {});
      };

      if (!document.visibilityState || document.visibilityState === "visible") playVideo();
      if (document.addEventListener) {
        document.addEventListener("visibilitychange", function () {
          if (!document.visibilityState || document.visibilityState === "visible") {
            playVideo();
          } else if (video.pause) {
            video.pause();
          }
        }, false);
      }
    })();
  </script>
</SiteLayout>
